storyInfo:
Frostleaf's valiant efforts finally give a chance for Amiya a chance to break through, and everyone is able to retreat at last.
However, when they return, they quickly find out that Lungmen itself is in grave peril...

attributes.content: Meteorite! We've managed to push the Yeti Squadron back!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: I seem to have underestimated you, Rhodes Island.
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: Perhaps I held back a bit too much.
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: (I can't feel my fingers anymore... Damn it...)
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: The cold current... is still gathering around her?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Is she trying to absorb all the ice surrounding us and release it at once? !
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: ...She's going to drain all the heat from our bodies!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: These Arts are on a complete different scale from what we saw before...!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Let it all come to an end.
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: May your anger be buried by purest frost.
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: Something... is stopping the cold from gathering...
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: I won't let you... come any closer...!
attributes.name: Frostleaf

attributes.content: ...Did you disrupt my cold current using your own Arts?
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: Frostleaf used her blade to sever the cold current...!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: But, but... she can't hold out long in that condition!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Her blade... it's about to break!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: What?! The enemy is... rushing towards us?
attributes.name: Reunion Member

attributes.content: No, she's... she's going straight towards FrostNova?!
attributes.name: Reunion Member

attributes.content: Don't worry, it wasn't a direct hit!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: She, she's still able to run?!
attributes.name: Reunion Member

attributes.content: I told you! You'll never reach the Yetis!
attributes.name: Reunion Member

attributes.content: Keep firing! Don't give her an opening!
attributes.name: Reunion Member

attributes.content: Nooo!! She... she was hit... It can't be...
attributes.name: Jessica

attributes.content: ...It's just a scratch! You'll have to do better than that if you want to stop me!!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: More... I need to do more...
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: (The flow of the cold air... fluctuated for a moment?)
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Wait... Where is that flow coming from...
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: I'll just have to give this a try!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: She shattered the Originium we planted with her Arts?
attributes.name: Reunion Member

attributes.content: I knew it! FrostNova created that cold current by planting Originium!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: I... I promise to save you!!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Up here! Quick! Hold on to me!
Who said you could play the hero?!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Do you think I could just sit there and watch you die?
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Put me down... I'm not... some pet...
attributes.name: Frostleaf

attributes.content: I won't let go of you!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Everyone, let's get out of here!
attributes.name: Jessica

attributes.content: Meteorite, go ahead with Frostleaf. I'll cover your retreat!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Don't die... don't you dare die on me!!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Don't worry... you can't get rid of me that easily...
attributes.name: Frostleaf

attributes.content: Jeez, both you and Amiya too! Why do both of you have to be like this?!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: No matter how strong you might be... you're both just kids after all!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: You're still treating me like a kid...?
attributes.name: Frostleaf

attributes.content: ...If I could save all of you by giving up my life, I think that's a pretty good deal.
attributes.name: Frostleaf

attributes.content: You... Mark my words! If you ever try to do something like this again...
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Evacuate this area immediately! Protect the medics and the injured!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Snipers...! Aim at those effigies. Keep firing!!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Disrupt their formation! Demolish the entire building to cover our escape!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: The explosions are making the haze thicker...!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Everyone, we're retreating from this square!!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: How long have you been watching?
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: These warriors are worthy of praise.
Your body isn't in very good condition.
...I don't need you to remind me.
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: Just do what you need to do, old timer.
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: I'm going to go after Rhodes Island.
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: We have to get rid of them first. Only then, will we be able...
attributes.name: FrostNova

attributes.content: We're almost at the escape point.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: ...Amiya!! We've finally gotten through to the L.G.D.!!
attributes.name: Meteorite

attributes.content: Madam Ch'en? Can you hear me clearly?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: ...Reunion took over one of our important facilities and is now forcefully opening a passage between the slums and the outer city.
attributes.name: Ch'en

attributes.content: W managed to lure Lungmen and Rhodes Island right into our trap.
attributes.name: Mephisto

attributes.content: That's right. They won't be able to escape. Faust and Crownslayer have already broken their defenses at one location.
attributes.name: Mephisto

attributes.content: As you said, this will be our opening to flood into Lungmen.
attributes.name: Mephisto

attributes.content: We will set up ambushes around every corner. The road to Lungmen will run red with fresh blood.
attributes.name: Mephisto

attributes.content: Right, that old flag-waver should be coming back to Chernobog soon.
attributes.name: Mephisto

attributes.content: Do you have any other orders for me, Talulah?
attributes.name: Mephisto

attributes.content: ...to turn this rotten city into ashes.
attributes.name: Talulah
